longBusinessSummary: JNC Resources Inc. explores for mineral resources in Canada. It has an option to acquire a 100% interest in the Imperial property located in Esmeralda County, Nevada. The company also holds interests in the Malebo and Solomons properties located in New South Wales, Australia. JNC Resources Inc. was incorporate in 2019 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
